{"word":"Motive","slug":"motive","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Motive</b> Ascribed to God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=8'>Psa 106:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=36&verse=22'>Eze 36:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=36&verse=32'>Eze 36:32</a><br/> Right, required<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=18'>Mat 6:18</a><br/> Sinful, illustrated by Cain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=7'>Gen 4:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=12'>1Jn 3:12</a><br/> Misunderstood:<br/> - The tribes of Reuben and Gad:<br/> b in asking inheritance east of Jordan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=33'>Num 32:33</a><br/> b When they built the memorial<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=22&verse=34'>Jos 22:34</a><br/> - David's, by King Hanun<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=3'>2Sa 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=19&verse=4'>1Ch 19:4</a> <br/> - The king of Syria's, in sending presents to the king of Israel by Naaman<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=7'>2Ki 5:7</a> <br/> - Job's, in his righteousness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=1&verse=11'>Job 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=2&verse=5'>Job 2:5</a> "}]}